  <brief_title>Effect of a Self-care Intervention on Depression in People With Age-related Macular Degeneration or Diabetic Retinopathy</brief_title>
  <official_title>Effect of a Self-care Intervention on Depression in People With Age-related Macular Degeneration or Diabetic Retinopathy</official_title>
